beer.beer_description:
Who doesn’t like a good process? Turns out One Drop Brewing Co do, just as much as us. This imperial sour has god-knows how many steps and would have had a few more thrown in for good measure if we hadn’t had to brew via distance. 

The result is the berry crumble of sours packed with over 100g of Blackberry per tin and a healthy dose of Vanilla to round it all out.

Brewed by distance with our friends One Drop Brewing Co for our 1st Birthday.
